sequenceDiagram
    participant CS as Charging Station (OCTT)
    participant CSMS as CSMS (System Under Test)

    Note over CS,CSMS: Test Case: TC_B_20_CSMS
    Note over CS,CSMS: Reset CS - Without ongoing transaction - OnIdle

    Note over CSMS: Manual Action: Request CSMS to reboot CS<br/>with type OnIdle

    CSMS->>CS: 1. ResetRequest (type: OnIdle)

    CS-->>CSMS: 2. ResetResponse (status: Accepted)

    Note over CS: CS reboots

    CS->>CSMS: 3. BootNotificationRequest

    CSMS-->>CS: 4. BootNotificationResponse
    Note over CSMS: Validation: status must be Accepted

    CS->>CSMS: 5. StatusNotificationRequest + NotifyEventRequest
    Note right of CS: connectorStatus: Available

    CSMS-->>CS: 6. Responses
